{
    "Body": " CryptoGlobe is looking for freelance copywriters to cover cryptocurrency-related news articles and opinion blogs. There may also be opportunities for candidates to help develop content strategy and fulfil an editorial role if desired. The ideal candidate will: Be able to cover breaking and complex cryptocurrency topics. Have strong written communication skills Have the ability to work well with a team to coordinate and execute the content strategies Have extensive SEO knowledge Have active social media accounts to share content. The copywriter will be expected to: Write clear and concise news stories on the cryptocurrency industry Improve source articles by including extra facts, charts, quotes and links Maintain strict journalistic values Cover breaking stories on a timely basis Work closely with a team of freelance writers to organize and choose newsworthy content Work with editorial team to be consistent with CryptoGlobe style Have a deep understanding of the cryptocurrency markets as well as the latest technological developments Research complex topics and present them clearly and concisely Edit and proof content Drive traffic using SEO and social media strategies Please send a CV and a portfolio of previous work. While CryptoGlobe is based in London, UK and Lisbon, Portugal, we are open to remote workers. Please tell us why you love crypto in your cover letter : ) About us: CryptoGlobe is a fast growing cryptocurrency news site that launched in late February 2018. We strive to be a trusted source for the latest news and analysis in the crypto space. Our mission is to educate and entertain the public by delivering accurate and high-quality news and information. We publish pertinent news articles and thought-provoking opinion pieces written by contributing writers around the world. Skills Writing, Editing, Social Media Marketing Compensation Fee per article ", 
